---
title: Parts
description: "`parts:` declares sub-artifacts of a composite artifact. Short IDs + `label:` show how opaque keys pair with human-readable names."
artifact:
  D0: { label: Source }
  D1:
    label: Release Package
    parts: [D2, D3, D4]
  D2: { label: Binary }
  D3: { label: Config }
  D4: { label: Release Notes }
process:
  P1: { label: Build }
---
D0 >> P1 -> D1
